          .modal-body
            %h2 Arcis
            %p.item-intro.text-muted A cross between an arcade and RTS game
            =image_tag "arcis_full.png", class: "img-responsive img-center"
            %p
              Arcis is the largest personal project that I have created to date. This game
              was my first large-scale Android project and the first that had any semblance
              of an artifical intelligence system. I reverse engineered A* pathfinding
              to improve performance and allow all of the enemy units to navigate together.
              Testing was done through major Reddit croudsourcing and I received incredibly
              valuable feedback for the creation of the final product.
            %p
              %strong What to play the game?
